a":"Can I pay by card?"},{"tipo":"traducir","enunciado":"¿Cuánto cuesta?","respuesta":"How much is it?","aceptadas":["how much is it"]},{"tipo":"traducir","enunciado":"¿Puedo pagar con tarjeta?","respuesta":"Can I pay by card?","aceptadas":["can i pay by card"]}]}
